      hr
      br
      p
        strong May 15, 2024
      p
        | Last week, I sat down with Hugo Bowne-Anderson from the 
        a(href='https://vanishinggradients.fireside.fm/26') Vanishing Gradient
        |  to record a podcast all about LLMs. We ended up covering the entire LLM lifecycle, what type of skills you need to work with them,
        |         what type of resources and hardware, prompt engineering vs finetuning vs RAG, and more! (Plus, I gave a 30 min live demo finetuning an LLM for classification). You can find a link to the podcast 
        a(href='https://vanishinggradients.fireside.fm/26') here
        |  and a YouTube video version 
        a(href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qL4JY6Y5pmA') here
        | .
