      p
        | I somehow made it to GitHub&apos;s top-1 spot on the Trending Developers list.
        | I&apos;ve been coding on GitHub quite consistently for about 12 years, but I honestly never expected to find myself up there!
        | As a passionate coder and open-source developer, this is perhaps the nicest compliment for me so far!
