      hr
      br
      p
        strong Mar 19, 2024
      p
        | I had the pleasure of sitting down with Jon Krohns on the
        a(href='https://www.superdatascience.com/podcast/open-source-llm-libraries-and-techniques-with-dr-sebastian-raschka') SuperDataScience podcast
        |         for what turned into a roughly 2-hour mega interview on LLMs. We covered pretty much everything! 
        br
        a(href='https://youtube.com/watch?v=CyprtaOZxu0')
          picture
